{"tid":1598380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實講五區革命d人，係咪無預過和理非份？","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:41:52.000Z","uid":4875,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee42cad94454996baaf468633aebc626ede584e","tid":1598380,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"你地話五區集會，但你地要知道，好多都係一家大細同和理非，佢地大多只會參加有一個固定路線的遊行，因為佢地要確保安全！<br />\n<br />\n我想問五區集會，當日會做d咩，去邊？確保到佢地會肯出黎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我知連登仔好多都係勇武，但唔好再活係自己世界！<br />\n要顧及和理非/有小朋友，只要夠人多，班狗就唔會做到咩！</span>"},{"pid":"ae72dddd328871c25bc76a9ea764769f6794ab54","tid":1598380,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c3b894d84252a0474da980c052e19872df7524c","tid":1598380,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"466fcca0def013eb73c93d555d3ff58aae32c66e","tid":1598380,"uid":169836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"696db621050970d44bc3aa30d9ab54af9c88e08c","tid":1598380,"uid":183734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQcNM8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQcNM8f.jpg&h=6830aa04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FewrieW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFewrieW.jpg&h=6d60f315&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f73d94440d08be6e77bb95701d05665d28c57965","tid":1598380,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43cd05af6968ae7ce7458ee33c6ca5b01e83924c","tid":1598380,"uid":63045,"